title: Jewish Trivia Contest, David Dobrik & Scotty Sire - Frenemies #24
description: On this episode of Frenemies Ethan and Trish discuss the fallout from Scotty Sire's goofy Dobrik defense vid, secret DM's from influencers, Trisha being too hard on Dixie, and they have a contest on who is the true king of all Jews!
